author: andreas
msg: Pass usecase name as parameter to usecases.js. This allows to invoke the flowscript in different ways than just using a request parameter.

author: rickhall
msg: Modified config.properties file substitution to allow for nested property
substitution, which makes it possible to initialize the system bundle
export package property with the appropriate set of JRE packages.
Modified the config.properties file to include reasonably complete
JDK 1.5 packages, but 1.3 and 1.4 are incomplete. (FELIX-78)
